Author: OodietcokeheadoO
Text: Obviously I can't diagnose you, but I do feel like ED's are able to creep into your life with or without being worried about your weight or calories. I think it will always find a way to manifest itself and find a reason you shouldn't eat/purge/overeat/under eat be it money, weight, religious reasons, health reasons it will find a was to present itself in your life. That's just my 2 cents though...
